title: Dealing with Divorce with Laura Wasser
itunes:title: Dealing with Divorce with Laura Wasser
description:
Attorney, author, host of the podcast All's Fair with Laura Wasser, and founder and CEO of the online divorce service It's Over Easy Laura Wasser herself drops by to talk about divorce, moving on, quarantine and the evolution of dissolution.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
